
Andy:

	Add the following for the adx_ccd_control prog:

	Change Energy option:

	  Never:

		No change to the command stream.

	  Each Run:

		mad run
		mad_wave wave1 wave2 ... waven

	  Each Anom Wedge:

		mad wedge
		mad_wave wave1 wave2 ... waven

	  Every blah frames:

		mad frames blah
		mad_wave wave1 wave2 ... waven

    
    Put out on the mad_wave however many wavelengths are active;
no need to provide a count.

		Chris


